description:
In this episode we learn about Jesus' baptism and experience in the wilderness. Jesus' public ministry began with him finding John the Baptist and being baptized, after which he was taken to the wilderness for 40 days of fasting and prayer. This was followed by Satan tempting Jesus to try and derail his mission at the very start, but thankfully he was not successful.
